Raspberry pi: 
    a. open camera and  keep capturing what is happening near by for every 15 seconds. 
    b. send the timestamp and descrption to the server. 
    c. Suppose a gun or leopard is seen, then live video stream starts, for 2 minutes.
IITB SERVER
    a. store the time stamp and as well as description into the csv file
    b. csv handler will make the decription to store in csv database
    c. This CSV is used later to make RAG, daily summary RAG application etc. 